Class TestInvertedIndexIO

java.lang.Object
  de.aitools.invertedindex.core.TestInvertedIndexIO

public class TestInvertedIndexIO
extends java.lang.Object

The purpose of this unit test is to ensure the basic functionality of IndexBuilder und IndexSearcher. More extensive tests are available in the C++ source code (aitools3-invertedindex-cpp).
